Package es.upm.dit.gsi.shanks.agent.exception

Exception Summary
DuplicatedActionIDException Indicates that an action with the given identifier has been already added to the simulation engine.
DuplicatedAgentIDException Indicates that an agent with the given identifier has been already added to the simulation engine.
DuplictaedDisplayIDException Indicates that a display object with the given identifier has been already added to the simulation grpahics engine.
UnkownAgentException Indicates that an agent with the corresponding ID cannot be found on the hole simulation.
